    <item>
      <title>英国大选前，斯塔默警告不要推行美国和欧洲的民粹主义</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/starmer-warns-against-us-europe-populism-ahead-of-uk-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默表示，尽管欧洲和北美的右翼政党崛起，但工党领导的英国不会在世界舞台上陷入孤立。他警告称，只有进步政党“才能应对”世界面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/starmer-warns-against-us-europe-populism-ahead-of-uk-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 13:26:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国极右翼德国选择党在暴力冲突中支持联合领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/german-far-right-afd-party-backs-co-leaders-amid-violent-clashes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在埃森举行的代表大会上，德国选择党代表们搁置内部纷争，重新选举了该极右翼政党的联合领导人并赋予其更强的权力，与此同时，数万名抗议者聚集在会场外，部分抗议者与警方发生了冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/german-far-right-afd-party-backs-co-leaders-amid-violent-clashes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 13:26:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默称不会为促进经济增长而策划银行税突击行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/starmer-says-he-won-t-plan-bank-tax-raid-in-bid-to-boost-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国反对党领袖基尔·史塔默 (Keir Starmer) 表示，工党注重增长，因此不打算提高英国银行的税收。在距离他出任首相的选举不到一周之际，这位反对党领袖试图安抚金融业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/starmer-says-he-won-t-plan-bank-tax-raid-in-bid-to-boost-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 13:25:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙进入选举决战阶段，勒庞难以击败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/macron-heads-into-election-showdown-as-le-pen-looks-hard-to-beat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃马纽埃尔·马克龙呼吁法国人民“书写历史”，这一呼吁将于周日成为现实，届时选民将前往投票站参加第一轮立法选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/macron-heads-into-election-showdown-as-le-pen-looks-hard-to-beat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>毛里塔尼亚即将成为天然气生产国，领导人寻求连任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/mauritania-leader-seeks-reelection-as-nation-s-set-to-become-a-gas-producer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[毛里塔尼亚现任总统很可能在周六的选举中获得第二任期，这为投资者提供了对这个即将成为天然气生产国的欧盟盟友的政策连续性的保证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/mauritania-leader-seeks-reelection-as-nation-s-set-to-become-a-gas-producer</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
